---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Glow Trading">
	<main>
		<h1>About Glow</h1>
		<section class="content">
			<p>Glow is pioneering the intersection of quantitative analysis and men's beauty, creating personalized solutions that take the guesswork out of skincare and grooming.</p>
			
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>To empower men with data-driven beauty solutions that deliver measurable results through innovative algorithms and personalized recommendations.</p>
			
			<h2>Our Approach</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Advanced analytics for personalized skincare</li>
				<li>AI-powered routine optimization</li>
				<li>Data-driven product recommendations</li>
				<li>Quantitative measurement of results</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Why Quantitative Beauty?</h2>
			<p>By applying quantitative techniques to beauty and skincare, we remove subjective guesswork and provide measurable, scientific approaches to achieving your best look.</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.content {
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	ul {
		margin: 1rem 0;
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	li {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}
</style> 